{"tid":1537381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話要贏，究竟點先可以贏？成日話咁200萬人，睇你拉得幾多？根本就錯logic","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T02:22:10.000Z","uid":268540,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8a848549f9c893281a8c56425ea0846ed87798","tid":1537381,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"200萬人只係人數上嘅優勢，成日話你拉得幾多？手足嚟㗎，日日咁拉，拉完又繼續上街，一個循環嚟，我地根本傷唔到佢地一條鳩毛。<br />\n次次都係企街對峙，咁最後又係畜牲小隊打鳩我地，再捉人。仲要對峙個陣武力唔對等，人又多咪變做靶囉。<br />\n根本打鳩休班警先可以取勝，我當200萬得100分之1係真勇武都夠打休班警啦。拉下拉下真係會冇曬，到時就輸，一輸，我地就會變新疆，美國最多只係助攻，自己香港，自己救。萬一香港冇咗經濟，美國同支共都會覺得香港已經冇利用價值，到時美國理得我地死啦，支共就會報仇。<br />\n香港人太多包袱，但係要贏就真係得呢個方法<br />\n太善良啦，係戰場上善良只係一個缺點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n革命唔同示威，大家要有推翻政府嘅心<br />\n遊擊同伏擊係我地贏嘅關鍵，只要突破我地嘅心理關口就係可以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n只要同狗賊做同一樣嘢，人數優勢先可以發揮出嚟<br />\n伏下一個，伏下又一個，3萬幾個幾警察好快就收佢地皮<br />\n另外所有魔法師可以地支持警方嚴正執法嘅遊行，玩魔法，因為咁係唔會俾人捉。又可以俾人睇到狗賊執法嘅不公"},{"pid":"56cf0d86cd3f9c9176369de2e18c306df36b5447","tid":1537381,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:03:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49017d6b799cf137ffe1c5de7675e97ca7b7507a","tid":1537381,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef88aea20593568172a5f6f367da86590defa510","tid":1537381,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcpj.jpg&h=145b357e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d48c1022306289c4ec0cf4162e7a131c31469775","tid":1537381,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:19:57.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"de510cbf39b3623bef2c852b6c35dc6ecca0bf6f","tid":1537381,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:20:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color